channel.title: Run.bat problem
channel.description:
So I'm working on a source then I compile it and I get this [Launcher] Initing Cache... Exception in thread "main" java.io.FileNotFoundException: data\cache\main_file_c ache.dat2 (The system cannot find the path specified) at java.io.RandomAccessFile.open(Native Method) at java.io.RandomAccessFile.<init>(Unknown Source) at java.io.RandomAccessFile.<init>(Unknown Source) at com.alex.store.Store.<init>(Store.java:25) at com.alex.store.Store.<init>(Store.java:19) at com.rs.cache.Cache.init(Cache.java:20) at com.rs.Launcher.main(Launcher.java:64) Press any key to continue . . .
; I tried everything to fix it, changing the location of the loaders, redoing my environmental variables, I even made sure none of the cache was missing but it wouldn't go away. If someone could please help me I'd very much appreciate it.
